description: The world’s dumbest characters are back, and they’ve gathered for an even bigger, dumber competition! Following the viral success of the original campaign, Dumb Ways to Die 2: The Games brings a massive set of new, action-packed mini-games to your Windows 8 device. Train safety has never been this hilariously frantic.
